{"tid":522811,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲格︰冇諗過賓特拿會踢森林","createTime":"2018-01-08T01:51:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T05:07:11.000Z","uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d06465f38624c963087130c8ab76854356b7737b","tid":522811,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T01:51:22.000Z","msg":"對於這位曾為兵工廠上陣171場的前鋒，雲格說︰「我對於他轉投森林有點意外，但他的確需要一個新開始，雖然<span style=\"color: red;\">這球隊不是他慣常的水平</span>，但其實他亦在伯明翰展開足球生涯，當時他做得很好。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「對於一些有質素的球員，他們只需要一個機會，他是個頂級球員，只欠一些比賽。或許有人認為他過分自信，但我不覺得是這樣，他在阿仙奴只是欠缺一點耐性，急於表現自己，這是可以理解。有時有些球員的問題我解決不來，便惟有放手讓其他人處理。」"},{"pid":"67c5174593d86f50f7e7c61ec94393d16e67c868","tid":522811,"uid":6070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T01:56:06.000Z","msg":"森林對nben嚟講太高水平"},{"pid":"3f9d060533ebf03cd6e9c177da116c3b0b0f617a","tid":522811,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67c5174593d86f50f7e7c61ec94393d16e67c868","tid":522811,"uid":6070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T01:56:06.000Z","msg":"森林對nben嚟講太高水平"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T02:01:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76151eab74aeb200fdf4abd8c4e3de4b64a3d4a4","tid":522811,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f9d060533ebf03cd6e9c177da116c3b0b0f617a","tid":522811,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67c5174593d86f50f7e7c61ec94393d16e67c868","tid":522811,"uid":6070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T01:56:06.000Z","msg":"森林對nben嚟講太高水平"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T02:01:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T02:55:08.000Z","msg":"屌用錯ac"},{"pid":"4eef49238fcf14256391ab669caa4f17ee86479f","tid":522811,"uid":111006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76151eab74aeb200fdf4abd8c4e3de4b64a3d4a4","tid":522811,"